t for `spring-boot-starter-logging`.\n\nManual next steps:\n1. Confirm whether `org.springframework.boot:spring-boot-starter-logging:2.6.3` should be treated as out of scope for reachability metadata because it is a starter descriptor with no JVM classes.\n2. If that classification is correct, close or re-triage this request as `not-for-native-image` instead of trying to generate tests for the starter itself.\n3. If support is still desired, open a new request for the actual class-bearing dependency that needs metadata (for example one of the logging implementation artifacts pulled in by the starter) rather than the starter coordinate."}}
